{"componentChunkName":"component---src-layouts-blog-post-layout-js","path":"/blog/impulse-theme-thumbnails-mobile-product-page","result":{"pageContext":{"id":538,"date":"2021-03-14T14:55:02","date_gmt":"2021-03-14T14:55:02","guid":{"rendered":"https://www.ezfy.club/?p=538"},"modified":"2021-03-16T00:46:09","modified_gmt":"2021-03-16T00:46:09","slug":"impulse-theme-thumbnails-mobile-product-page","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https://www.ezfy.club/impulse-theme-thumbnails-mobile-product-page/","title":{"rendered":"Enable mobile thumbnails for product pages on the Impulse Theme"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>The impulse theme by Archetype Themes, by default, does not come with an option to show thumbnails on mobile devices. With some minor custom coding it&#8217;s possible to achieve that, though.<br><br>This code was tested on Impulse version 3.4.0.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Safety first: making a backup copy of your theme</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Before diving into the tutorial make sure you download the theme, so in case you face any issues you can easily revert back.<br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1514\" height=\"481\" class=\"wp-image-503\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123.png 1514w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-600x191.png 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-1200x381.png 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-768x244.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1514px) 100vw, 1514px\" /></p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Showing the thumbnails on mobile</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>In your Shopify admin, go to&nbsp;<strong>Online Store</strong>&nbsp;&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Themes&nbsp;</strong>&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Actions&nbsp;</strong>&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Edit Code</strong>.</li><li>Find the file named <strong>product-images.liquid</strong></li><li>Press CTRL + F (or CMD + F if you are on Mac) and search for <strong>small&#8211;hide</strong></li></ol>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1200\" height=\"591\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image-2-1200x591.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-539\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image-2-1200x591.png 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image-2-600x295.png 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image-2-768x378.png 768w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image-2-1536x756.png 1536w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image-2.png 1613w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" /></figure>\n\n\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li>You should find only one occurrence of this. Make sure you delete the word and click on&nbsp;<strong>save</strong>.</li>\n</ol>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1200\" height=\"594\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image-3-1200x594.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-541\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image-3-1200x594.png 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image-3-600x297.png 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image-3-768x380.png 768w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image-3-1536x760.png 1536w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image-3.png 1616w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Editing the javascript file</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Find the file named <strong>theme.js</strong></li><li>Press CTRL + F (or CMD + F if you are on Mac) and search for this:<br><br><strong>initSliders:</strong> <br><br>Don&#8217;t forget to include the colon on your search (the two dots on top of each): <strong>:</strong></li><li>Again, you&#8217;ll find only one occurrence, like the image below shows.<br><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1585\" height=\"831\" class=\"wp-image-543\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/imp1.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/imp1.jpg 1585w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/imp1-600x315.jpg 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/imp1-1200x629.jpg 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/imp1-768x403.jpg 768w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/imp1-1536x805.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1585px) 100vw, 1585px\" /></li><li>Delete everything below the line you found (<strong>initSliders</strong>) until this symbol: <strong>},</strong> <br><br>It should look like this:<br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1567\" height=\"794\" class=\"wp-image-545\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/imp2.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/imp2.jpg 1567w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/imp2-600x304.jpg 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/imp2-1200x608.jpg 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/imp2-768x389.jpg 768w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/imp2-1536x778.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1567px) 100vw, 1567px\" /> </li><li><a href=\"https://gist.github.com/dpw1/f853cfa40b6be224b240a0be7a2c5f59\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Open this link</a> and copy the code.<br><script src=\"https://gist.github.com/dpw1/f853cfa40b6be224b240a0be7a2c5f59.js\">&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;lt;/</script></li><li>Paste it below below the line you found (<strong>initSliders</strong>) and click <strong>save. </strong>It should look like this:<br><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1572\" height=\"864\" class=\"wp-image-549\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/imp3.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/imp3.jpg 1572w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/imp3-600x330.jpg 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/imp3-1200x660.jpg 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/imp3-768x422.jpg 768w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/imp3-1536x844.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1572px) 100vw, 1572px\" /></li></ol>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">The final, quick step</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>From your Shopify admin, go to&nbsp;<strong>Online Store</strong>&nbsp;&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Themes&nbsp;</strong>&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Customize</strong></li><li>Navigate to <strong>Product Pages &gt;</strong> <strong>Product Pages</strong><br><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"757\" height=\"447\" class=\"wp-image-554\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/imp4.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/imp4.png 757w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/imp4-600x354.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 757px) 100vw, 757px\" /></li><li>Make sure <strong>thumbnails position</strong> is <strong>below media</strong><br><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"483\" height=\"764\" class=\"wp-image-556\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/imp5.png\" alt=\"\"><br></li><li>Now save and you&#8217;re ready to go!</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Display thumbnails on mobile devices at the product page for Archetype&#8217;s impulse theme.</p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":558,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[9],"tags":[209],"image_alt":"","featured_image_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Debut-Slider-Pro-7-600x338.png","featured_image_small_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Debut-Slider-Pro-7-100x100.png","featured_image_large_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Debut-Slider-Pro-7-1200x675.png","categories_names":["Blog"],"acf":[],"tag_names":["impulse theme"],"featured_image_url":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Debut-Slider-Pro-7.png","featured_image_url_alt":"","_links":{"self":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/538"}],"collection":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/types/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/users/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/comments?post=538"}],"version-history":[{"count":8,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/538/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":568,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/538/revisions/568"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/media/558"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/media?parent=538"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/categories?post=538"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/tags?post=538"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https://api.w.org/{rel}","templated":true}]}}},"staticQueryHashes":["330429198","3356652627"]}